<HEADLINE> Pak Speaker Leaves for Seoul for Inter-Parliamentary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, April 7 (Xinhua) -- Speaker of Pakistan's National
Assembly Ellahi Bakhsh Soomro left here today for Seoul with a
parliamentary delegation to attend the 97th Inter-Parliamentary
Conference.
</P>
<P>
Soomro said before his departure that he will try his utmost to
establish close ties with speakers of member countries of the
Inter-Parliamentary Union.
</P>
<P>
He also said that he will actively pursue the agenda for the
establishment of a union of legislative assemblies from Muslim
countries.  
</P>
</TEXT>
