<HEADLINE> German, Spanish Police Uncover Drug Ring </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, April 7 (Xinhua) -- German and Spanish police have
uncovered an international drug trafficking ring and seized 30
kilograms of cocaine, German police said today.
</P>
<P>
