replacement and possibly Bayern Munich's Giovanni Trapattoni will
be the head coach for next season.
</P>
<P>
Liedholm, who left his native Sweden for Italy and AC Milan in
1949, won four league titles as a player (1949, 1950, 1960 and
1961), before starting his coaching career with Milan.
</P>
<P>
He took them to the league championship in 1979, before guiding
Roma to the title in 1983, along with three Italian Cup successes
(1980, 1981, 1983) and a European Cup final in 1984 before ousted
on penalties by Liverpool. Enditme

