<HEADLINE> Chinese Conference on Radio &AMP; TV Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 8 (Xinhua) -- The China Radio &AMP; Television
Society (CRTS) held its third meeting on radio and television work
in Beijing today, to discuss radio and TV programming in China.
</P>
<P>
Sun Jiazheng, Minister of Radio, Film and Television, said at
today's opening that, since its founding, CRTS has played an
important role in programming, improving management, and training
people, and in establishing and developing socialist theory on
radio and television with Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
