world over to act and stop interruptions by Israel of the
activities of Palestinian political bodies and disgracing the
dignity of the Palestinian Council members.
</P>
<P>
As the Palestinian Council failed to convene in Ramallah
today, it decided to put off the session until Wednesday. It is
not clear whether the Israeli authorities have promised to
permit the Gaza members to leave Gaza and enter West Bank
Wednesday or not.
</P>
<P>
The total closure imposed by Israel on the Palestinian
territories following the Tel Aviv suicide bombing last month
remains in force. The Israeli authorites warned that more
terrorist attacks are in the offing. 
