Alfred James Obita, the Lord's Resistance Army's (LRA) Secretary for
External Relations and Mass Mobilization, had preliminary talks
Sunday in London when they took part in Acholi Tribe International
Conference at which Obita announced the willing of Joseph Kony, LRA's
leader, on peace talks the previous day.
</P>
<P>
