<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, April 8 (Xinhua) -- Eighty-eight Tamil rebels have
been released after their rehabilitation at Sri Lanka's Youth
Redevelopment and Training Center in the north of the country,
according to the Defense Ministry today.
</P>
